npc:23:23:4:4:objects\npc.ogg:"If you have mud on your boots, wipe them before you track village filth across my floorboards."
npc:4:4:4:4:objects\npc.ogg:"In my day, people stood straighter and spoke less. Two habits this village could stand to recover."
npc:43:43:4:4:objects\npc.ogg:"Do close the door properly. Drafts are for barns, not respectable homes."
npc:10:10:13:13:objects\npc.ogg:"If you need a quiet place to breathe, stay near the bookcase. Father seldom wanders that far."
npc:14:14:20:20:objects\npc.ogg:"You look pale. Sit a moment, and I'll bring tea before someone notices and makes it unpleasant."
npc:22:22:15:15:objects\npc.ogg:"Well, you don't look particularly important, do you? I suppose that must be freeing."
npc:28:28:20:20:objects\npc.ogg:"One day this village will appreciate a commanding presence. Until then, it has me."
npc:36:36:15:15:objects\npc.ogg:"If this is another family conversation, wake me when it becomes worth hearing."
npc:42:42:20:20:objects\npc.ogg:"Careful what you repeat outside this house. Stories travel faster when I give them a push."
npc:10:10:24:24:objects\npc.ogg:"Why is everyone always whispering? If they have complaints, they can line up and complain properly."
npc:22:22:34:34:objects\npc.ogg:"You may address me as Mayor Holloway, and you may keep this brief. A household of importance does not run itself.|What you see here is forty years of careful management. You are welcome to observe from a respectful distance.|If you have business with the village, bring it in writing. Loose words accomplish nothing and leave even less."
object:18:32:8:10:A broad dining table groans under trays, silverware, and enough food for a house that never learned moderation.:objects\table.ogg
object:4:10:18:20:A deep upholstered sofa sits near the hearth, chosen more for status than comfort.:objects\sofa.ogg
object:4:8:13:15:A tall bookshelf is packed with untouched histories, legal codes, and expensive bindings bought for show.:objects\bookshelf.ogg
object:38:46:12:14:A polished television chatters softly in the corner, speaking to no one in particular.:objects\tv.ogg
object:40:46:32:34:A heavy iron oven radiates a steady heat from the back of the room.:objects\oven.ogg
object:20:28:24:26:A cabinet full of ledgers, petitions, and sealed letters. Most of them seem to be filed to impress visitors rather than to help anyone.:objects\paper.ogg
object:4:10:32:34:A luxurious guest bed with far too many pillows.:objects\bed.ogg
door:25:25:0:0:data\maps\village.map:152:45:You step back outside in front of the mayor's house.:misk\doorsnd.ogg:misk\dooractivate1.ogg:true:false
